Class Account

java.lang.Object
Account
Direct Known Subclasses:
Checking, Credit, Savings
abstract class Account
extends java.lang.Object
Account Class is an abstract class that holds certain information about a bank account, with this information the user is able to perform certain actions with the information that range from making a balance inquiry, transfer, deposit, withdrawal, or payment on that specific account
Since:
March 15,2021
